1
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:19,820
Legend of Awakening

2
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:22,579
Episode 36

3
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:35,920
Yan Family is famous for sword.

4
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:39,800
Today my son will inherit the Sword of Yan

5
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,280
as well as Wuji Manor.

6
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,560
Congratulations, younger master.

7
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,120
What’s up, Old White?

8
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,120
Sword.

9
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,380
The man with the sword.

10
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,560
It was him.

11
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:13,120
He killed my brother.

12
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:22,760
Old White.

13
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,000
Father.

14
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,340
Who is that?

15
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:28,800
Lu Ping.

16
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,400
How come it’s you?

17
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,520
Kill him.

18
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,560
Kill him.

19
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,040
You promised me!

20
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,680
Old White.

21
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,320
Kill him.

22
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,940
As expected, it’s you.

23
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,060
You are the murderer 19 years ago.

24
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,440
Murderer?

25
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:42,000
Master Yan is the murderer?

26
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,930
What is going on?

27
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:43,960
Lu Ping.

28
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,160
What did you say?

29
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,000
Who is he?

30
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,800
People from Shanhai Gang have sneaked into Longjie Army.

31
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,680
Take them down.

32
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,170
We have enough time.

33
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,890
I, as the son of Leng Xiutan,

34
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,000
will take revenge on you.

35
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,000
Go.

36
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:03,840
Kill him.

37
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:05,800
A Ze.

38
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:06,660
Chase them.

39
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,810
General Wen,

40
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,130
what’s going on?

41
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,760
Ask your respected father.

42
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:28,640
Master.

43
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:30,960
Guests have been settled.

44
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,080
But younger master

45
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:34,120
said he would like a walk.

46
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,200
What about Ling Ziyan?

47
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:37,120
Miss Ling has been in her room

48
00:04:37,320 --> 00:04:38,840
without crying or shouting.

49
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:41,240
She said she would wait for younger master.

50
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,440
A sensible girl.

51
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:45,290
What about younger master?

52
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,280
He is confused.

53
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,800
He will come back.

54
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:49,680
Leave us alone.

55
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,040
Yes.

56
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:53,880
Master.

57
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,680
We have divided disciples into more than ten teams

58
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,520
and searched around Wuji Manor.

59
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,560
We didn’t find Lu Ping.

60
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,850
And Princess Xining

61
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,760
has been back in her camp.

62
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,920
She seemed to have been hurt.

63
00:05:08,080 --> 00:05:09,280
Continue the searching.

64
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,440
Send all our men

65
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,720
and stop them from gossiping.

66
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,840
We should say it is the plot of Shanhai Gang.

67
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:19,040
Lu Ping was lured by Liu Song.

68
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,360
This is the only version of the story.

69
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:21,920
Yes.

70
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:30,920
Go out then.

71
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,159
Yes.

72
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,159
Come out now.

73
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:57,560
Being my son, you shouldn’t be so upset.

74
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:58,720
Father.

75
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:02,810
Don’t you think that you should explain to me?

76
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,530
You always have your reason

77
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,080
when doing everything.

78
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:16,330
There was a time when I left home

79
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,700
but you never tried to find me.

80
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,960
I know that you wanted me to grow up.

81
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,020
But I don’t understand

82
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,720
what happened today.

83
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,520
You didn’t keep Lyu Chenfeng

84
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,520
for his own safety.

85
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,120
Right?

86
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,120
No.

87
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,570
What about Lu Ping and Qin Sang?

88
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:41,240
Did you want to kill them?

89
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,640
I should have killed them in person.

90
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:48,900
Then I would not have troubles like this.

91
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,600
The brother mentioned by Lyu

92
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,400
who was killed by you

93
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,040
was the master of Big Dipper,

94
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,700
Leng Xiutan, right? He’s also Lu Ping’s father.

95
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:07,600
Yes.

96
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:10,880
Father.

97
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,800
You said his parents were

98
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,400
killed by Shanhai Gang.

99
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,360
That is correct.

100
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:20,680
I started Shanhai Gang.

101
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:26,450
I don’t understand.

102
00:07:29,280 --> 00:07:31,080
Since we have talked about this,

103
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:34,240
I will tell you the truth.

104
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:44,800
More than ten years ago,

105
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,320
Wuji Manor didn’t exist in Jianghu.

106
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,840
In Jianghu,

107
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:54,040
seven masters of Big Dipper were the most famous.

108
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:07,200
Master Leng Xiutan was excellent at Force of Sound.

109
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:11,480
His wife Shao Yinchu was a wonderful woman.

110
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:13,960
She was good at sword.

111
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:18,480
I ranked second for Sword of Yan.

112
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,240
The rest.

113
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,560
Chu Min and Guo Youdao

114
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,850
can use both Forces of Heft and Air.

115
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,880
Liu Song was the last to join us.

116
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:38,030
He was noble and good at Force of Spirit.

117
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:43,640
Chenfeng was the youngest.

118
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,200
He was mentally ill.

119
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:48,800
But he was a genius at
Forces of Temperature and Air.

120
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,480
He could create weapons.

121
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,400
Brother Leng was kind and amiable.

122
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,280
He loved his wife very much.

123
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:03,800
And he took good care of us.

124
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,880
We seven were

125
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,680
young and beautiful

126
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,560
at that time.

127
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:16,360
Once,

128
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,880
I met His Majesty

129
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:21,400
on my way to see you and your mother.

130
00:09:22,520 --> 00:09:24,880
He was just a young guy then.

131
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,880
But he was knowledgeable and brave.

132
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:29,680
We talked for a night

133
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:32,040
and became friends with each other.

134
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:37,600
Brother Yan is skilled.

135
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:40,280
It is a pity if you don’t use

136
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,600
your skills to create a country.

137
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,040
You have such a far-reaching ambition.

138
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,840
I will try to persuade Big Dipper

139
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,160
into helping you

140
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:53,840
and your father.

141
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,800
At that time,

142
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:04,680
many competitors appeared in succession.

143
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,360
Everyone wanted to

144
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,680
be somebody,

145
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,920
even your father.

146
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,680
But Brother Leng

147
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,240
didn’t think so.

148
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:34,560
Brother.

149
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,000
I lost again.

150
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:37,360
Qiuci,

151
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,160
your sword is vigorous.

152
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,280
You will surpass me

153
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,860
in less than two years.

154
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:45,640
Brother,

155
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,810
I have something to say.

156
00:10:48,640 --> 00:10:50,300
The war has been too long.

157
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,400
Now people all compete for the throne.

158
00:10:52,400 --> 00:10:54,360
There is no peace even in Jianghu.

159
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:57,160
It’s our chance to show ourselves.

160
00:10:57,840 --> 00:11:01,600
We can interfere into the political affairs.

161
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,120
When I came back,

162
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,170
I met Zhai Wei and Zhai Rong.

163
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,760
They are leading an uprising.

164
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,360
Many people supported them.

165
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:12,280
We can help them with the assistance

166
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,160
of men from other sects in Jianghu.

167
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,440
I believe that in the future…

168
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:15,960
Enough.

169
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,090
Don’t talk any more.

170
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:20,320
I disagree.

171
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,240
Brother.

172
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:24,580
Our master taught us martial skills.

173
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,880
Should we have meaningless practice

174
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,880
here every day?

175
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:31,240
I have told you many times.

176
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,680
Big Dipper never interferes into politics.

177
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,120
We are to spread martial skills.

178
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,600
There have been many dynasties

179
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,520
during 100 years,

180
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,420
but we have only one

181
00:11:43,760 --> 00:11:44,840
Big Dipper.

182
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,080
Brother.

183
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:50,000
No one can stay out of it in the war.

184
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,760
If people in Jianghu

185
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:56,280
work for the court,

186
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:59,760
they will lose their pride.

187
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:03,600
We don’t want to interfere

188
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:05,330
and we can’t interfere.

189
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:08,880
Yes.

190
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:13,930
Brother.

191
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,090
Brother.

192
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:15,680
See.

193
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,780
I made a suit of armor for Ping’er.

194
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,040
Chenfeng.

195
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,440
You are now the Master of Tianquan Peak.

196
00:12:26,440 --> 00:12:28,040
You should learn martial skills.

197
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,570
Brother.

198
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:30,360
It’s OK that I can’t use martial skills.

199
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:32,320
I have you here.

200
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,280
Creating weapons is more

201
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,520
meaningful than learning skills.

202
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,920
If you are always the master here,

203
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:39,050
I will create weapons for you forever.

204
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:40,920
Moreover,

205
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:44,120
Ping’er can protect me after he grows up.

206
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:46,040
He must be more skilled than me.

207
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,440
Don’t let the child fall.

208
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,040
Let me.

209
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,320
He is strong.

210
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,280
The child was

211
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:54,760
Lu Ping?

212
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:55,920
Yes.

213
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:59,680
Brother was a nerd of martial skills.

214
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:02,240
He didn’t care about others.

215
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,240
After the birth of such a talented boy,

216
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,600
he cared only about Lu Ping.

217
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:11,050
Big Dipper could be nothing

218
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:12,720
under his management.

219
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:18,080
I was young

220
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,760
and angry.

221
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,280
Thanks to me,

222
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,560
Big Dipper could be that strong.

223
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,210
It was because he was the master

224
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,560
that I couldn’t realize

225
00:13:31,560 --> 00:13:32,800
my ambitions.

226
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,140
Therefore,

227
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,280
I had been waiting for my chance

228
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,680
until I found

229
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:44,280
the secret of Liu Song one day.

230
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:53,040
At that time, Liu Song just entered Big Dipper.

231
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,600
He didn’t say about his identity.

232
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:59,040
I just felt he was noble

233
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:02,520
and mysterious.

234
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,600
Once, I heard

235
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:08,120
him talking with brother.

236
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,080
Today,

237
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:12,920
I got caught by you.

238
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,000
I have nothing to say.

239
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,760
Please do anything

240
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,600
as you like.

241
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,040
I can forgive you.

242
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:33,440
But Big Dipper never interferes into politics.

243
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,520
You have two ways to go.

244
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:37,920
Firstly,

245
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:40,010
you will be the prince of Dan

246
00:14:40,040 --> 00:14:41,840
if you go down the mountain now.

247
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:45,440
You are no longer one of us.

248
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,080
Secondly,

249
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,640
you stay here

250
00:14:49,880 --> 00:14:52,360
and you are no longer the prince.

251
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,560
You are just Song of Tianji Peak.

252
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:58,240
We will be with you.

253
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:00,360
And, you should give out Thousand Pine ruler

254
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:03,320
and the commander’s seal

255
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:06,570
to prove your determination to stop the warfare.

256
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:09,200
Follow me.

257
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:15,240
According to my investigation,

258
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:17,880
Liu Song who said he was interested in skills

259
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:19,880
and came to learn martial skills

260
00:15:20,760 --> 00:15:23,120
was actually a prince of Dan.

261
00:15:23,300 --> 00:15:25,740
[Big Dipper Institute]

262
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:27,760
It was my only chance.

263
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:32,000
I found Zhai Rong.

264
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:39,760
It is a good time.

265
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:41,960
What did you prepare

266
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:44,640
in exchange of the cup of tea?

267
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:47,760
Liu Song is in Big Dipper.

268
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,520
But Leng Xiutan cares about him.

269
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,840
With Leng,

270
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,450
you can’t kill Liu Song.

271
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,280
I can help you

272
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,200
to get the seal.

273
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,040
What do you want?

274
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:04,640
A new start and chance.

275
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:19,480
Deal.

276
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:23,960
Big Dipper opened its door

277
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:27,960
to all the sects for skill exchanges.

278
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,280
In order to get the seal,

279
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:32,360
I made Chu Min and Guo Youdao away

280
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:34,400
when brother and sister-in-law

281
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:37,320
took Ping’er down the mountain.

282
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:41,080
Only Liu Song and Chenfeng were in.

283
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:45,240
I pretended to leave,

284
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:47,770
saying I was to see you and your mother.

285
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,130
Zhai Rong and his men

286
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,720
disguised as a sect

287
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:56,000
and came in.

288
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,720
They were for the seal.

289
00:16:58,660 --> 00:17:02,380
[Big Dipper Institute]

290
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:01,520
I named the sect Shanhai Gang

291
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:04,720
in order to

292
